Minimum Profit README
=====================

 Minimum Profit - Programmer Text Editor
 Copyright (C) 1991-2006 Angel Ortega <angel@triptico.com>
 Home Page: http://www.triptico.com/software/mp.html
 Mailing List: mp-subscribe@lists.triptico.com

This is an EXPERIMENTAL version for evaluation purposes only. See
the RELEASE_NOTES file for more information.

Compiling & Installing
----------------------

	 $ ./config.sh
	 $ make
	 # make install

Apart from the usual building packages, you also need flex and
yacc (or bison).

